This act shall take effect as follows and shall amend the following
sections:
Section 1 October 1, 2026 14-296aa
Sec. 2 October 1, 2026 14-222
Sec. 3 October 1, 2026 14-36(e)(3)
Sec. 4 October 1, 2026 14-1(88)
Sec. 5 October 1, 2026 42-110x(a)(15)
Statement of Purpose:
To (1) specify a video or moving image that is visible to a driver while
seated in the normal operating position constitutes distracted driving,
and (2) make distracted driving in a highway work zone a reckless
driving violation.
